PUERTO ANGEL

A coastal vampire town in southern Mexico, reachable south from the
Illinois Road south of Chi-Town (long wasteland route).

Key areas:
  Outskirts, Main Street, Cantina, Residential District,
  Abandoned Church (silver cross), Beach, Harbor.

Day vs night:
  The town is sealed and empty by day. After nightfall (server UTC proxy),
  vampires prowl the streets and harbor. Some may not look like what they are.

Combat notes:
  Vampires are MDC creatures. Use MDC weapons or magic.
  The church is a safe rest spot; vampires avoid it.
  The hunter in the cantina sells advice, not miracles.

Route from Chi-Town:
  chitown_burbs -> illinois_road -> (south, long) -> pa_outskirts

See also: combat, death
